&lt;p&gt;Stefania has a PR open for her &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-11731&quot; title=&quot;dtest failure in pushed_notifications_test.TestPushedNotifications.move_single_node_test&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-11731&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-11731&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; fixes &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/riptano/cassandra-dtest/pull/983&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. I don&apos;t see a PR for your added test. Do you want to OK the 11731 PR and PR your added test on commit &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=beobal&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;beobal&quot;&gt;beobal&lt;/a&gt;, or do you want me to?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15339486" author="beobal" created="Mon, 20 Jun 2016 13:32:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks! committed to 2.2 in &lt;tt&gt;142f358f6958695c4248acb94b89b64e95ccc609&lt;/tt&gt; and merged to 3.0/trunk. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve also merged Stefania&apos;s dtest PR and opened a &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/riptano/cassandra-dtest/pull/1049&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;second&lt;/a&gt; for my additional test.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
